com.gussssy.gametwo.game.objects

Class Charachter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gussssy.gametwo.game.objects.GameObject
      • com.gussssy.gametwo.game.objects.Charachter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NPC, Player

    public abstract class Charachter
extends GameObject
    Extension of momentum to group all charachter game objects. Charachter Game objects include the player and NPCs - They move around the game enviroment. - They are effected by forces: gravity, explosions, platforms etc Possible future feature: They have mass and momentum.
